trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeParameter"></xref> objects.
The CodeTypeParameterCollection class provides a simple collection object that can be used to store a set of <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeTypeParameter> objects.
Initializes a new, empty instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeParameterCollection"></xref> class.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeParameterCollection"></xref> class containing the specified array of <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeParameter"></xref> objects.
An array of <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeTypeParameter"></xref> objects with which to initialize the collection.
